### 1. Intake turn
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/intake/turns
Content-Type: application/json

< ./requests/01-intake-turn.json

### 2. Proposal draft
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/proposals
Content-Type: application/json

< ./requests/02-proposal.json

### 3. Patchset candidate
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/patchsets
Content-Type: application/json

< ./requests/03-patchset.json

### 4. Preview
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/previews
Content-Type: application/json

< ./requests/04-preview.json

### 5. Compile intent
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/intents/compile
Content-Type: application/json

< ./requests/05-compile-intent.json

### 6. Replace IDs from responses and inspect
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/debug/semantic?execution_id={{execution_id}}
